name: Good Lunch DAO
description: Ever dreamed of dining with the legendary Warren Buffett? This might just be your chance! ‘Good Lunch Dao’ is holding a crowdfunding campaign to enter the auction for this year’s “Power Lunch with Warren Buffett”. Anyone can donate to the fund for a chance to meet Warren! At any time during the first-round funding period (funding up to the 500 ETH milestone) you can use your $GL as proof to redeem 100% of your donated funds.
